bibl.title: Catalogue of British Museum Objects from the Egypt Exploration Fund's 1913/14 Excavation at Antinoupolis (Antinoë).
bibl.note: The 75 objects catalogued constitute a representative sample of objects excavated by John de Monins Johnson on behalf of the EEF at ancient Antinoupolis in 1913/14.
